title: TENGERR - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents TENGGER performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded October 23rd, 2023.

Songs:
Eunhasu
Panaptu
Achime
Exhale

Marqido - Synth / Electronics
Raai - Synth / Vocals
